<link href="adcp.css" rel="stylesheet"><entry><xh5>every now and then • now and then</xh5><p> <i>every now and then—</i>fairly often; habitually: <u>Every now and then</u> a motion picture comes along so permeated with suspense as to make the spectator sit tense in his seat.</p><p> <i>now and then—</i>occasionally; at times: After he retired, he enjoyed spending a lot of time reading at the public library. <u>Now and then</u> he would take a trip.</p> </entry>
